        <updateDate>2009-04-15T19:15:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Property Tax Relief Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow state and local real property taxes paid on a principal residence as a deduction from gross income (thus allowing taxpayers who do not itemize their tax deductions to claim such deduction).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Property Tax Relief Act of 2009</title>
